00:01:48.000 --> 00:01:57.000
But I think Jonghyun has various kinds of voices. So I felt more comfortable when singing.

00:01:58.000 --> 00:02:02.000
Giving and taking. They were busy praising on each other. 

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:10.000
No need to speak. We were able to confirm their harmony through this one stage. 

