00:02:56.000 --> 00:03:03.000
I am in the group EXO which is the youngest team in EXO and today I will be on stage with SM seniors today so I will do my best.

00:03:11.000 --> 00:03:16.000
I was only able to hear their harmonious voice through the album but I am so moved by sincerity after listening to the music directly from them.

